Winetricks is an easy way to work around problems in Wine.

It has a menu of supported games/apps for which it can do all the workarounds automatically. It also allows the installation of missing DLLs and tweaking of various Wine settings.

== USE flags ==
{{USEflag|package=app-emulation/winetricks}}

== Installation == 
<code>emerge -a =app-emulation/winetricks-9999</code>

It's not recommended to emerge non-9999 version of winetricks due verification issue from upstream.

